channel.title: PI hybrid pvp v3 help
channel.description:
1) smelting, how to do 5x / 10x / or a custom number picked by a player for smelting your bars. at the moment u can only smelt one at a time
2) could someone make me a small code to add this small prevention of auto clickers.. Every stall has a 8-15 times stole from the stall possibility of you getting caught, when your caught you get hit randomly between each stalls numbers randomly. Stall 1 - randomly 1-2 damage Stall 2 - randomly 1-3 damage Stall 3 - randomly 1-4 damage Stall 4 - randomly 2-5 damage Stall 5 - randomly 3-6 damage
